<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="/public/stylesheets/home.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <title>홈 페이지</title>

    <style>
        *{
    font-size: 14px;
    }
    .login{
    width:1040px;
    height: 624px;
    position: absolute;
    left:50%;
    top:50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 4px 0px #00000040;
    background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.048);
    }
    .login:active{
    background-color: rgba(236, 198, 128, 0.067);
    }
    .imgLogo {
    width: fit-content;
    margin: auto;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 200px;
    }
    .textHome{
    display: block;
    width: fit-content;
    margin: auto;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 25px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: darkgray;
    text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .left{
    position: absolute;
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    }
    .right{
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    right: 0%;
    background-color: #fff;
    }
    .llogo{
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 40px;
    }
    .lbtn{
    width:290px;
    height: 50px;
    margin:20px;
    border:none;
    background-color: #2F6C2461;
    }
    #logingo{
    text-decoration: none;
    background:none;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #fff;
    }
    #llink{
    background-color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #2F6C24;
    }
    .btn {
    margin-left: 430px;
    margin-top: 110px;
    background-color: #ebd6cb;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 20px;
    }
    .btn:hover{
    border-left: 3px solid brown;
    }



    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="/index">
        <div class="login">
            <img class="imgLogo" src="../img/logo.png">
            <p class="textHome">주문을 하시려면 화면을 터치해주세요!</p>
        </div>
    </a>
    <div class="admin">
        <a class="btn" href="/login">관리자 전용</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 